channel.title: winterFisson - Packaged by Stupit
channel.description:
[size=12pt][b]winterFission[/b][/size] [center][img]http://i30.tinypic.com/30db62r.png[/img][/center] One of the cleanest servers out there. client.java only 60kbs. .rar file is only 92kbs. This is the packaged server if you would like the unpackaged server, check this link. [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,393211.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,393211.0.html[/url] A quote from one, programmer that i think will go far, Fission.
Well, Devo and me do not mix well. RS001 failed hard with all the bugs with Single-threaded... so, I am doing something cool. WinterLove, no, not a derivative, thee winterLove. I see a whole lot of people who are put off by WinterLove because it's packaged, basic, and just not "friendly." Personally, I believe that is a big lie. Packaging is better in my eyes. But, lets take a step back and make this user friendly for these people. Single-threaded, EventManager... Things like this (Btw, thanks for those Graham!) make advances, and help winterLove allot. So, the goal... Get this to a stable, small form factor, and release. Get the minimums, get them right the first time, get them working.
[b]Pictures[/b] [img]http://img32.imageshack.us/img32/5939/fissions.png[/img] [img]http://img32.imageshack.us/img32/7281/28440072.png[/img] [img]http://img41.imageshack.us/img41/5997/fis.png[/img] [i][b]Credits[/b][/i] 99% Fission 1% Stupit, for packaging and fixing 3 bugs ;p. [i][b]Download[/b][/i] [url=http://uppit.com/v/m8799t5y]http://uppit.com/v/m8799t5y[/url] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?wdmkotndkjy]http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?wdmkotndkjy[/url]
